{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"184-look-at-me","title":"Look At Me","description":"Meet the children in the book. They are just like you!","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"portrait","authors":["Manisha Chaudhry"],"illustrators":["Ajit Narayan"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/184-look-at-me"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/721874/size3/8ecac1b7b1c40058b7d2b62254e358d7.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/721874/size6/8ecac1b7b1c40058b7d2b62254e358d7.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2203/size6/0798d23c1915d1f7108b427dac4b6bcc.jpg","text":"Look at us.\nDo you want to be our friend?","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2204/size6/1388faf4b0f7b8090c1b64c4e829f979.jpg","text":"My legs are very strong.\nI can run really fast with them.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2205/size6/92e341944e694418e2bcfa771386758e.jpg","text":"And my arms... such a nice swing!","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2206/size6/57b5b3bf864b4dae340f7a6452aaa688.jpg","text":"I like to draw.\nI use my hands for drawing.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2207/size6/aaba74d944248484b76a4aa76d6e8944.jpg","text":"Should I draw your picture?\nI can see you with my eyes.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2208/size6/a8bda930c5d4a2f83a8a9f644b286b74.jpg","text":"The bird sings a sweet song.\nI can hear it with my ears.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2209/size6/2e780d0b33b878fcb3c74c44f224b06d.jpg","text":"I think Ma is making halwa.\nI can smell it with my nose.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2210/size6/6881cda9909510f20dc0fa8b81661265.jpg","text":"Oh! This sugarcane is so tough! But my teeth are strong too!","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2211/size6/891d1b7244852a8795e3ced7830f7228.jpg","text":"It is very sweet.\nMy tongue just told me.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2212/size6/91aba36897216808ba1e1e1fa93092e8.jpg","text":"I can sing.\nShould I sing you a song?","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2213/size6/e99eecf7730c3c4e21ac8ef8727a8b12.jpg","text":"Ma says I have a good voice. Does it come from my throat?","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":120}}